name: We Wish To Board At Once
Lore: 'Ambassadors carry a certain amount of political power. Jedi ambassadors carry a lot more.',
Text: 'Use 3 Force to take one Effect of any kind into hand from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Take Radiant VII, or one Interrupt with the word ''Podracer(s)'' in its game text, into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
